### Government

We know that there is a Wizengamot acting as a High Court[^20210329-1], an
International Confederation of Wizards[^20210329-2], and a Ministry of
Magic.[^20210329-3] The relationship between these and the powers of each is
largely speculative, especially if you use only the seven original books as a
reference.  

#### Ministry of Magic

* The Minister for Magic is democratically elected.[^20210330-6]
* Like the British parlament, there is no fixed term.[^20210330-7]
* Elections at least once every seven years.[^20210330-8]

